# =============================================================================
# Repository policy: track `.cursor/**`, root `README.md`, and this file.
# All other paths are excluded by the leading `*`. Re-apply exclusions under
# `.cursor/` for CHM / raw HTML so they are never committed inside the skills tree.
# =============================================================================

*

!.gitignore
!README.md

!.cursor/
!.cursor/**/*

# --- Revit API skill: keep packaged index only (no CHM / decompressed HTML)
.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/*.chm

.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/*

!.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/
!.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/symbols.jsonl
!.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/md/
!.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/md/**

.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/symbols.jsonl.bak.*
.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/symbols.jsonl.new
.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/md/.rename-stage-*/
